Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.16,0:01:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,THE CLASH OF LOVE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.59,0:01:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Needle Thousand!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.73,0:02:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no intention of sacrificing myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.24,0:02:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I intend to save Lord Hadorra instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.36,0:02:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Save?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.91,0:02:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, Lord Hadorra will die.\NNo one can stop that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.67,0:02:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But King Ban's Supercharged Dark Magic\Nmay be able to save Lord Hadorra.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.63,0:02:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I am going to defeat all of you myself\Nand then go to King Ban to beg a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.60,0:02:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So that he will save Lord Hadorra!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.60,0:02:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that something you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.81,0:02:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, this is of my own volition.\NI'm sure Lord Hadorra will be angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.27,0:02:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But Lord Hadorra's survival\Nis my greatest wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.95,0:03:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Albinass...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.12,0:03:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If you feel sympathy,\Nthen stop resisting and die quickly...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.38,0:03:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,oh, kind little Maam.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.00,0:03:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Needle Thousand!{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.19,0:03:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You're like a rat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.19,0:03:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't waste any more time\Non the likes of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.94,0:03:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The queen is a piece that rarely moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.53,0:03:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'll show you the form I take\Nwhen I fight at full strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.46,0:04:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hands?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.68,0:04:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's your true form?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.64,0:04:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The queen is the most powerful\Npiece in chess.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.65,0:04:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to hold back that power\NI normally disable my hands and feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.11,0:04:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I've taken this form,\Nyou have no chance of winning!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.79,0:04:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.58,0:04:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,My best spell is Begiragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.63,0:04:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Needle Thousand works by fragmenting\Nthis spell and emitting it from my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.72,0:04:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But when I use my hands,\NI can focus the energy in one spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.98,0:04:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I call it {\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Thousand Ball!{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.19,0:05:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Behoimi will hardly delay the inevitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.19,0:05:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's strong! Too strong!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.36,0:05:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With that much power, Albinass\Nmight really defeat all of us alone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.74,0:05:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.99,0:05:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Albinass...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.92,0:05:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.17,0:05:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to fight you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.38,0:06:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Please reconsider!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.26,0:06:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're going to beg for your life,\Nat least admit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.97,0:06:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The emotion that drives you\Nto such a decision...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.39,0:06:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't just be loyalty, can it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.60,0:06:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.10,0:06:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What you feel for Hadorra is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.52,0:06:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to say that I love him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.57,0:06:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Spare me your nonsense.\NI am neither male nor female.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.95,0:06:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the queen! A mere chess piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.66,0:06:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,A piece is a tool of war!\NIt does not deserve to love anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.63,0:06:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Albinass!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.59,0:06:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence! Stop trying to buy time\Nto heal yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.10,0:07:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good. Stand still, just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.77,0:07:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's no good!\NNo amount of convincing will work!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.61,0:07:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're lost in their own emotions\Nand beyond reason!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.12,0:07:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What can I... What can I do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.58,0:07:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Good girl, Maam. Now go to the afterlife.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.76,0:07:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Thousand Ball!{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.59,0:07:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maam...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.76,0:07:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maam...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.76,0:07:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But Maam...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.06,0:07:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,there are times when love and kindness\Naren't enough to protect people.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.90,0:07:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as strength without justice\Nis powerless,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.45,0:07:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,so too is justice without strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.82,0:07:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.70,0:07:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't let myself be defeated here!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.83,0:08:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right. I also...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.54,0:08:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I also have...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.52,0:08:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Amudo!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.32,0:08:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Albinass, I will defeat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.99,0:08:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I also have people precious to me\Nthat I have to protect.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.29,0:08:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.22,0:08:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Ron Berku's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.01,0:08:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! Like Hyunckel's weapon,\Nthis Dark Armour Fist turns into armour!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.22,0:09:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And it makes me\Ncompletely immune to magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.89,0:09:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Until now, I couldn't\Nbring myself to use it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.10,0:09:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,because it's far too powerful!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.77,0:09:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't allow you to defeat me here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.53,0:09:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll fight to the fullest, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.82,0:09:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Albinass!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.95,0:09:24.54,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}REFRACTOR FIST{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.96,0:09:29.54,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4}NEEDLE THOUSAND{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.59,0:09:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridiculous! Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.43,0:09:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is why Ron Berku told me\Nto wear it on my non-dominant hand!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.60,0:09:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It especially enhances\Nthe defense of the side it's on!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.57,0:09:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And with this Metal Fist...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.19,0:09:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It works!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.49,0:09:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even against Orichalcum, I can shatter it\Nif I have this much speed and hardness!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.79,0:10:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.88,0:10:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.17,0:10:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you think you could win\Njust by wielding that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.85,0:10:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Why can't I...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.29,0:10:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So fast... At this rate, I'll lose!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.58,0:10:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But Albinass is made of Orichalcum.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.09,0:10:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My Refractor Fist won't work!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.38,0:11:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll use the other skill\NGrand Master taught me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.76,0:11:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Warrior Master Style\NTiger Shatter Fist!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.64,0:11:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This attack is the most physically\Ndestructive attack I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.69,0:11:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You focus all your Aura into one point\Nand unleash it at a high velocity.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.91,0:11:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But you mustn't use it\Nunless absolutely necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.70,0:11:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The massive force it causes\Ncan reflect back on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.91,0:11:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With my Dark Armour Fist protecting me,\NI should be able to use it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.92,0:11:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? So you intend to stop flailing around\Nand want to use a single killing strike?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.43,0:11:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It will not change a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.69,0:11:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I still intend to try!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.56,0:11:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Even a brute\Nwho downs a bear in one strike
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.94,0:11:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,can die to a swarm of bees.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.78,0:11:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.54,0:12:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.26,0:12:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}S-So strong!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.34,0:12:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This is your answer, Maam!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.85,0:12:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll keep hitting you\Nwhile moving at a high speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.44,0:12:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all I need to do\Nto slowly eat away at your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.40,0:12:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This fight is already over!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.50,0:12:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I see you've run out of strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.71,0:12:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You've proven quite troublesome.\NI'll praise you for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.38,0:13:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The queen truly is strong!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.80,0:13:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But why?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.01,0:13:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With this sort of power,\Nwhy didn't Albinass use it before?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.93,0:13:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This battle could have\Nbeen won much sooner...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.35,0:13:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So why?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.61,0:13:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The queen is a piece that rarely moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.52,0:13:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The queen is indeed the strongest piece.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.61,0:13:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But its extreme mobility\Ncan be its downfall.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.61,0:13:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's it! That's my only option!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.41,0:13:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You've accepted your fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.09,0:13:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, as you wish,\NI shall pierce your chest!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.80,0:13:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, Maam!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.72,0:13:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll quickly send your friends after you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.61,0:14:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,H-How...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.86,0:14:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You're fast, but even you\Ncan't dodge that many projectiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.99,0:14:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And due to your extreme speed,\Nthe collision caused overwhelming damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.71,0:14:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the queen's weakness!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.25,0:14:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,On my back,\Nyou could only attack from the front.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.13,0:14:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You charged straight into\Nthe fragments I shattered!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.39,0:14:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You've lost, Albinass!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.27,0:14:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.65,0:14:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.40,0:14:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Forgive me, Albinass!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.99,0:14:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my final attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.87,0:14:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Warrior Master Style Secret Attack...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.96,0:15:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Tiger Shatter Fist!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.31,0:15:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I've won!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.70,0:15:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Come no closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.04,0:15:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I have lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.58,0:15:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that\Nunderestimating you cost me my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.34,0:15:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Albinass.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.51,0:15:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,With my core penetrated,\Nmy body will soon explode.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.22,0:15:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me, Albinass.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.31,0:16:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.81,0:16:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You need not feel sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.28,0:16:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,If you hadn't won,\NI would have killed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.44,0:16:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You were just stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.03,0:16:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Not just in power,\Nbut in your drive to help others.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.46,0:16:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.54,0:16:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a shame. It's regrettable.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.76,0:16:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems, in being\Na piece that was created,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.55,0:16:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,my will could never be\Nas strong as a human's.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.14,0:16:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Hadorra...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.35,0:16:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted him to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.56,0:16:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For even a moment, even a second longer.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.15,0:16:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if it cost me the life he gave me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.74,0:16:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Now go from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.12,0:16:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And witness in my place...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.37,0:17:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Hadorra's final glory.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.63,0:17:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Albinass, you were more\Nthan just a chess piece.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.05,0:17:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What you felt for Hadorra...\NI'm sure it was...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.48,0:17:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}what humans call "love."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.86,0:17:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Bloody Sukuraido!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.65,0:17:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}D-Dammit!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.37,0:17:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I-I won't lose! I still haven't lost!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.96,0:17:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hym, you weren't weak.\NYou were just unlucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.63,0:17:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You faced me right after\NI awakened to a new power.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.55,0:17:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.68,0:18:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You defeated Albinass?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.85,0:18:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to Ron Berku's Dark Armour Fist.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.77,0:18:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I just defeated Hym.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.31,0:18:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like they're trying to buy time\Nfor Hadorra to fight Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.69,0:18:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.66,0:18:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hurry back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.08,0:18:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.25,0:18:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Popp.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.42,0:18:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He's fighting...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.13,0:18:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The knight, Sigma!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.84,0:18:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sigma has the Mirror of Shahal\Nthat can reflect any spell!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.67,0:18:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If Popp uses Medoroa...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.72,0:18:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you worried about Popp?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.81,0:18:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.94,0:18:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be. Even I couldn't\Neasily defeat Popp now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.44,0:18:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Even at a disadvantage, not even\Na Royal Guard-level enemy could beat him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.78,0:18:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.\NWe should trust Popp's abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.25,0:19:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam, why are you so concerned for Popp?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.38,0:19:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If it were me or Dai,\Nyou wouldn't feel this conflicted.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.30,0:19:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But you and Dai are really strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.10,0:19:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You always pull through on your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.14,0:19:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But Popp...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.52,0:19:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp's strong, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.52,0:19:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,he's always so careless without help.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.44,0:19:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to watch at times.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.19,0:19:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.11,0:19:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's how I've always looked at Popp!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.70,0:19:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's why Popp\Ntried so hard to get stronger!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.66,0:19:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was because of me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.34,0:19:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.59,0:19:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.14,0:20:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember what Popp said?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.14,0:20:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Your power is love.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.72,0:20:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Your love saved me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.35,0:20:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm truly grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.36,0:20:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But there are two kinds of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.23,0:20:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Loving someone to help them\Nand loving someone for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.74,0:20:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Loving someone for yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.61,0:20:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You always love others\Nout of a desire to help them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.62,0:20:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You have the spirit of Love.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.08,0:20:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But after this battle is over,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.54,0:20:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll eventually come to\Nlove someone for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.79,0:20:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Like how Miss Amy loves you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.96,0:20:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Though I can never reciprocate her love,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.26,0:20:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I can somewhat understand how she feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.47,0:20:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Love is an emotion beyond control.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.90,0:20:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It can at times lead people astray.\NLike how Baran and I fell to evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.61,0:21:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Like how Meruru and Albinass\Nwere willing to sacrifice themselves.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.28,0:21:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.37,0:21:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If you feel any emotion for Popp\Nthat you can't describe,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.46,0:21:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,then go find out for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.42,0:21:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave Dai to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.13,0:21:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.21,0:21:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp is still waiting for an answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.35,0:21:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Hyunckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.10,0:21:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maam... The angel of Love\Nwho gave me light.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.03,0:21:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Go on and find love for yourself.\NNot just for everyone else.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.87,0:21:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And find happiness.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.16,0:21:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can never bring you happiness.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.18,0:22:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To be honest I was clumsy{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.18,0:22:12.06,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}omoeba boku wa bukiyou de{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.22,0:22:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And it took me forever to get here{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.22,0:22:18.40,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}shouganaikurai tomawarishita{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.90,0:22:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I used even loneliness as a weapon{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.90,0:22:23.86,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kodokukannsura mo buki ni shite{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.03,0:22:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I searched the dungeon for a simple answer{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.03,0:22:29.78,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tannjun na kotae wo sagashita dannjon{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.95,0:22:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if I cast aside\NRightness and kindness{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.95,0:22:35.62,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tadashisa yasashisa nagedashite mo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.79,0:22:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I just want to be there for you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.79,0:22:41.75,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tada hitori kimi no mikata de itai{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.92,0:22:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To call out your name{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.92,0:22:47.38,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kimi no namae wo yobu koto ga{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.55,0:22:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is harder than any magic spell{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.55,0:22:53.39,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ari to arayuru mahou yori muzukashikute{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.56,0:22:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even though you're so close to me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.56,0:22:59.19,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}konnani mo chikaku ni itanoni{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.35,0:23:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I love you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.35,0:23:01.81,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}aishiteiru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.98,0:23:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I finally realized it{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.98,0:23:05.11,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}imasara kizuitanosa{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.28,0:23:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To call out your name{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.28,0:23:10.24,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kimi no namae wo yobu tame ni{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.41,0:23:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Must be the reason I was born{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.41,0:23:16.66,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}boku wa kitto umarete kitannda{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.83,0:23:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I shake off the clinging night{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.83,0:23:22.58,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}shigamitsuku yoru furihodoite{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.75,0:23:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And go to see you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.75,0:23:25.30,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ai ni iku{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.46,0:23:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right now to where you are{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.46,0:23:30.05,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ima sugu kimi no moto e{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.68,0:23:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The battle between\NMaam and Albinass ended tragically,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.73,0:23:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but Maam's strong will led her to victory.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.98,0:23:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Meanwhile, Popp fights\Nan evenly matched battle with Sigma,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.57,0:23:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but he has no counter against Sigma's\NMirror of Shahal which reflects magic.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.65,0:23:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As the two continue to face off,\Nboth sides attempt a gambit.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.45,0:23:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,DRAGON QUEST The Adventure of Dai{\i1},{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.87,0:23:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Victory or Annihilation"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.79,0:23:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The adventure continues!{\i0}
